summary: Just a small mod if you can call it that of male presets at least one for each race.
descriptionHtml:
[u]= PLEASE READ =[/u]
[u]Depending on the mods you have installed will depend on how they will all look. [/u]

[font=Georgia][size=3]NOW WITH PICTURES! :)[/size][/font]

[font=Arial]Please enjoy the interestingly colorful combination of facial features, ages, looks, hair colors, styles and eye colors! Not a single one of them looks the same, minus the fact he may be a tad old. Each man ranges from 21 - 55 for most few go to 70 there should be an age, body type and look to match any one of your gaming style needs! [/font][font=Arial][size=3]Each and every male is hand made to use for playing around with these are just basic presets to build from, or use yourself. There is only one in this pack called Exon that is a so called "Pretty boy" and has been customized from head to toe. These are all for Vanilla races so sorry cupcake no custom races here, but what they lack in looks they make up for in numbers the Nord preset has 4 whooping presets! Each labeled for what preset it is please mind you that these are the ones I have since as said it will depend on the mods you have will change they're looks.

[/size][/font]Please note that each preset number is based on statics of how much each race is played.
author: GriffinSKMods
